    tags: ["Bahíyyih Khánum", "Greatest Holy Leaf", "Love", "Forgiveness", "Steadfastness"],
    summary:
      "Marjory Morten’s Bahá’í World tribute remembers Bahíyyih Khánum’s unconditioned tenderness, quiet courage, and radiant freedom from self.",
    source:
      "https://bahai.works/Bah%C3%A1%E2%80%99%C3%AD_World/Volume_5/The_Passing_of_Bahiyyih_Kh%C3%A1num%2C_the_Most_Exalted_Leaf",
    image: "",
